node.text:
We all know how our frontline workers have been helping us but getting a glimpse of the true reality and extent of this through the #TouchOfCare film has instilled a much stronger sense of gratitude in me. 
We should all express our thanks to Dr. Bhosale and many such doctors who did not quiver to extend their touch of care towards our nation. More power to Mrs. Bhosale who's now going to ensure that the little kids of Latur don't fall short of this care. On this National Doctors Day, let us ensure that we continue to fight this on-going battle and keep the doctors care alive.
@vicks_india #TouchOfCare

#ad
